---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Edukasi | Haikal Luthfianino">
    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 w-full">
        <div class="mb-12 border-b border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-900 pb-8">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-black dark:text-white tracking-tight mb-4">Edukasi.</h1>
            <p class="text-neutral-500">Perjalanan akademis dan pembelajaran formal saya.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="pl-6 border-l border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 space-y-12 relative">

            <div class="relative group">
                <div class="absolute -left-[30px] top-4 h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-black dark:bg-white ring-4 ring-neutral-50 dark:ring-neutral-900 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-125"></div>

                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
                    <div class="w-16 flex-shrink-0">
                        <img src="/unsap.png" alt="Logo UNSAP" class="w-full h-auto object-contain" />
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black dark:text-white mb-1">S1 Informatika</h3>
                        <h4 class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 font-medium">Universitas Sebelas April (UNSAP) Sumedang</h4>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-code mb-4 shadow-sm backdrop-blur-xl saturate-150 bg-white/40 dark:bg-black/40 border border-white/60 dark:border-white/10 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">
                    <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 animate-pulse shadow-lg shadow-emerald-500/50"></span>
                    Semester 4 (On-going)
                </div>

                <p class="text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
                    Mempelajari fundamental ilmu komputer dan rekayasa perangkat lunak. Fokus riset pada penerapan algoritma K-Nearest Neighbor (KNN) untuk sistem pakar diagnosis kegagalan perangkat keras.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="relative group mt-12">
                <div class="absolute -left-[30px] top-4 h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-neutral-400 dark:bg-neutral-700 ring-4 ring-neutral-50 dark:ring-neutral-900 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-125"></div>

                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
                    <div class="w-16 flex-shrink-0">
                        <img src="/smkpgristrj.png" alt="Logo SMK PGRI Situraja" class="w-full h-auto object-contain grayscale opacity-80 group-hover:grayscale-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-500" />
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black dark:text-white mb-1">Teknik Komputer & Jaringan (TKJ)</h3>
                        <h4 class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 font-medium">SMK PGRI Situraja</h4>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-code mb-4 shadow-sm backdrop-blur-xl saturate-150 bg-white/40 dark:bg-black/40 border border-white/60 dark:border-white/10 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">
                    <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-neutral-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
                    Lulus Tahun 2024
                </div>

                <p class="text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
                    Mempelajari dasar-dasar infrastruktur IT, mulai dari perakitan komputer, troubleshooting perangkat keras, hingga konfigurasi dan administrasi jaringan. Pengalaman ini menjadi fondasi awal yang kuat dalam memahami arsitektur sistem operasi dan low-level hardware.
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>

